Package com.halloween.view

Class View

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.halloween.view.View
  • public class View
extends Object
    Represents the data to be displayed to the user in a game. This class is a part of the View component as this program follows the MVC model.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor Description
      View()
      Initializes an instance of View, using JSON data in game-instructions- and NPC-dialogue-related files.
